description: Automate Twitter/X social media workflows including posting, engagement, analytics, and audience growth
version: 1.0.0
author: Claude Office Skills
category: social-media
tags:
  - twitter
  - x
  - social-media
  - marketing
  - engagement
department: marketing
models:
  - claude-3-opus
